creator: Sprout Wellness Solutions Inc
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Sprout Mobile

The health and wellness app that centralizes your health activities, identifies at risk areas, and rewards healthy behaviour. Connect with colleagues and encourage or compete with one another to achieve your health goals. Share your success on the social wall and monitor your progress with our wellbeing score.

With Sprout you have the freedom to create your own events, challenges, and build your wellness community.

Please note. To use the Sprout app your company must be an active Sprout customer and enrolled in our mobile program.
descriptionShort: Get fit together with Sprout at Work!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- An updated dashboard to provide a more personalized experience
- Support for automatically detected activities from wearables
- General improvements and bug fixes

title: Sprout @Work

creator: Sprout Wellness Solutions Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Healthy doesn’t need to be hard!

The Sprout at Work mobile app is your place to realize your wellbeing goals and connect with colleagues. With Sprout, you can identify at-risk areas, set targets, track activities and be rewarded for healthy behaviours. Get social and enjoy motivating wellness-based challenges.

- Connect with colleagues on the social stream and community groups
- Sync your activity from Apple Health, Fitbit, Garmin, and more
- Set recommended and personal health goals
- Monitor your health progress with our wellbeing score
- Challenge yourself and others in friendly competition
- Create events and invite your colleagues

Note: Your company must be registered with Sprout to use Sprout at Work.

The Sprout at Work mobile app is your place to realize your wellbeing goals and connect with colleagues. With Sprout, you can identify at-risk areas, set targets, track activities and be rewarded for healthy behaviours. Get social and enjoy motivating wellness-based challenges.

- Connect with colleagues on the social stream and community groups
- Sync your activity from Apple Health, Fitbit, Garmin, and more
- Set recommended and personal health goals
- Monitor your health progress with our wellbeing score
- Challenge yourself and others in friendly competition
- Create events and invite your colleagues

Note: Your company must be registered with Sprout to use Sprout at Work.
descriptionShort: Get fit together with Sprout at Work!
